olor:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">据不完全统计，农博会四天现场销售</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">5608.2</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">万元；</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">签订贸易合同金额</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">23.86&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">亿元，其中意向合同金额&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">13.41&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">亿元。现场销售额比上届翻了一番以上，贸易合同金额增长近百分之二十。展会上整个电商展区创造了</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">3500</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">万元以上成交额，达成意向合作订单总额超过</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">1000</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">万元。</span>'),(835,'5e10e031-2605-4a78-9f67-4e9c315e1b02','<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/UCMS/files/upload/ad1d10c1d161e7f7717622369116708f.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" title=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" />\n</div>'),(836,'5e10e031-2605-4a78-9f67-4e9c315e1b02','<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/UCMS/files/upload/4170ffe75315f78d9e48764f4a9992be.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" title=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" />\n</div>'),(837,'5e10e031-2605-4a78-9f67-4e9c315e1b02','<div style=\"text-align:cen